      <para id="id6621462">Activity 3</para>
      <para id="id17908773">To write down your own ideas [LO 4.1.2]</para>
      <para id="id17908777">WRITE YOUR OWN BILL OF RIGHTS</para>
      <para id="id17933367">Hints</para>
      <list id="id16915273" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>What would you like to change in the present Children’s Bill of Rights?</item>
        <item>What would you like to add to the Bill?</item>
        <item>What do you think children need that they are not getting NOW?</item>
        <item>Think of your own life and what right you wish you had which you don’t.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id7925409"/>
      <para id="id16748946"/>
      <para id="id16748949"/>
